{"tid":1696773,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急 今個星期日 屯門要人啊！！！","createTime":"2019-11-06T11:20:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-07T17:06:49.000Z","uid":220787,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7d150d656f7bba764e38fe890e0dc16646b25144","tid":1696773,"uid":220787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T11:20:32.000Z","msg":"屯門上星期無啦啦有陣tg味 政府無交代過<br />\n警犬是但係fb話唔係tg黎就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多小朋友聞完都唔舒服同咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後個晚要警方交代 佢地就放tg 拉左勁多手足<br />\n強硬入私人地方拉人 包括東屋台老闆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屯門牛牛！今個星期日！絕對要個合理交代！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔係屯門牛牛都歡迎大家黎啊</span></strong><br />\n好多人都唔知新和理係邊 姐係虹橋個球場啊！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vUYZMUL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvUYZMUL.jpg&h=45c672ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期日見！</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"940e55fcc4467af0a137575a49263f7fb5693fbb","tid":1696773,"uid":220787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T11:22:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LGWAkgZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLGWAkgZ.jpg&h=74caccbf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d50e01cd9e65294fdb6b73468d93ded5e191149a","tid":1696773,"uid":220787,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T11:22:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NsoK